Gauteng residents have been invited to share their views on what they expect from their government ahead of the tabling of the provincial budget by finance MEC Barbara Creecy. She will table her budget on March 6 and has called for input from residents on what the spending priorities in the province should be. Click on the following link to complete a quick survey where you can provide your input. It will take only about four minutes: >> Click here to do the survey You can also send more budget ideas to the MEC on Twitter at @BarbaraCreecyGP using the hashtag #GPbudget. This article was paid for by the Gauteng Treasury.